\id 1JN Tutsa: Bible Translation 1st Edition
\h 1 Joon
\toc1 JOON ih Takkhoh raang arah Le
\toc2 1 Joon
\toc3 1Jn
\mt1 JOON
\mt2 Ih Takkhoh Raang Arah Le
\imt1 Ephangjatjih
\ip \bk Joon ih takkhoh maat arah le, \bk* jaatnyi jengkhaap raangtaan ih raangta: Rangte nyia Hesah Jisu Kristo damdoh mamah ih roongtong theng ah erah wette loong suh tenchaan kot suh eno neng rang roomsoom ki nyootte loong dowa pui suh ban huk baat suh raangta, mongrep adoh mok woot woi tong ibah rangdah mina ang ih, erah raangtaan ih Rangte Sah Jisu ah timtok doh uh mina sah tajen ang thengta. Eki nyootte loong ih elang ih ah tumbaat rumta ah langla, khopui ah mongrep roidong raangtaan ih amah sah uh lathun thang ih tong ih doba pui ah; neng loong ih amah nep ih nyoot rumta, khopiipang abah ese reeraang nawa nyia mih minchan raangtaan ih choh ah ngeh ih tah angka.
\ip Arah nyootsoot ha ah daante rah ih phanjangjang phan baat ha Jisu Kristo ah mina amiimi angta, heh ih amah uh wakbaat eta, Marah ih Jisu nyia Rangte suh tuungmaang ha erah loong ih neng jaachi nah uh minchan mui jaatjaat etheng.
\iot Hemong Dowa Jatjih
\io1 Ephangjatjih \ior (1:1-4) \ior*
\io1 Weephaak nyia laamang \ior (1:5—2:29) \ior*
\io1 Rangte suh asah nyia Hakhoh juungbaan suh asah loong \ior (3:1-24) \ior*
\io1 Emoong nyia amiisak\ior (4:1-6) \ior*
\io1 Minchan mootkaat \ior (4:7-21) \ior*
\io1 Ejen etheng tuungmaang \ior (5:1-21) \ior*
\c 1
\s1 Roidong jengkhaap
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Jn 1:1\x* Roidong jengkhaap tiit sen suh raang kohi ah rangphang diidook eje angta. Erah seng ih echaat eti, eno seng mik ih nep tup eti; amiimiisak seng ih tup eti, eno erah seng lak ih nep thaak taajoot choi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Jn 1:14\x*Arah roidong ah mik etup theng ang thoidi, seng ih etup eti; erah raangtaan ih erah tiit ah baat hi, marah Hewah damdi angta lathoon roidong tiit nyia marah seng suh dong jatthuk hali erah ah.
\v 3 Marah kap tupti nyia marah kap chaatti erah tiit ah sen loong suh dong ja baat hi, erah doba seng loong damdoh heh Wah nyia heh Sah Jisu Kristo damdi rangsoom lom tongli adoh jen roongtong han.
\v 4 Arah seng\f + \fr 1:4 \ft Arah jengkhaap ah mararah le adi ba jeela \f* ten boot thoon roon suh raanghi.
\s1 Rangte ah weephaak
\p 
\v 5 Belam heh Sah jinnah wa chaatti tiitkhaap ah baat hi ah langla amah: Rangte ah weephaak, eno heh jiinni laamang tah jaatjaat jeeka.
\v 6 Erah ang abah heh damdi roongtongli liihi, eno rangnak nah moktong ibah, sengre sengraang nyia sengjeng sengkong ni eleek angli.
\v 7 Enoothong heh weephaak ni tongla likhiik seng uh weephaak nah tong ibah—seng loong ah rangsoom roongtong eli, eno heh Sah Jisu sih rah ih seng rangdah ah sa haat ehali.
\p 
\v 8 Seng loong ih seng rangdah tajeeka mokli ibah, seng teeteewah mokwaanhi, amiisak ah seng taang ni tajeeka.
\v 9 Enoothong seng ih Rangte suh seng rangdah ah biin anaan he mok baat ibah, heh kakham ah tah beehaat ka ang ah eno marah epun ah erah re ah: heh ih biin anaan ehe eno timthan ethih reeraang dowa seng loong ah saasiit ehe.
\v 10 Seng rangdah tah dake mok li ibah, Rangte ah eleek ngeh li hi, eno heh jengkhaap ah seng taang ni tajeeka ang ah.
\c 2
\s1 Kristo ah seng chosokte
\p 
\v 1 Nga sah loong sen suh arah raanghang rah sen loong naktoom dah kah an ngeh raanghang; Enoothong ngo dalu, erah raangtaan ih heh Wah reeni chuut huungte wasiit je ah—Erah langla kateng esiit, Jisu Kristo.
\v 2 Kristo heh teeteewah ah langla seng loong rangdah biin anaan theng lampo, seng loong rangdah luulu biin anaan tah angka, enoothong mongrep dowa thoontang rangdah biin anaan te uh elang eh ah.
\p 
\v 3 Rangte jengdang ah kap ibah, heh ah kamkam ih jat hi.
\v 4 Seng ih ejat ehi li eno heh jengdang ah lah chaat thang mok eh ibah, seng loong ah eleek eno amiisak ah seng taang ni tajeeka.
\v 5 Enoothong seng ih heh jengkhaap ah kap ibah, Rangte minchante epunthoon ah seng loong ah ang ih:
\v 6 Emah ang ino juuba seng Rangte damdi roong roopli ngeh ih kamkam ih jen ang ih, Kristo tongtha ta likhiik seng loong uh emah ih tongtheng.
\s1 Ena jengdang
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Jn 13:34\x* Nga mongnook joonte loong, arah ngah ih sen suh raanghang rah ena jengdang tah angka; arah ehak jengdang, marah ephang di sen jinni angta erarah ah. Ehak jengdang abah marah sen ih tiitkhaap ejen chaat etan erah angta.
\v 8 Ang abah uh, belam sen suh jengdang raanghang rah ena, mamah liidih amiisak tiit ah Kristo sak ni noisok ha ah likhiik sen sak ni nep uh noisok eha. Timnge liidih laamang ah jen mat eta, eno amiimiisak weephaak ah ejen phaak ela.
\p 
\v 9 Seng loong ih weephaak ni tongli li ino, phoh ano ah miksuk ruh mok eh ibah, amah dih uh seng ah laamang ni tongli.
\v 10 Seng ih phoh ano minchan eh ibah, seng loong ah weephaak ni tongli, erah raangtaan ih seng\f + \fr 2:10 \ft mararah adi marah marah mina taang ni raangha; \ft lah angka \fq seng taang ni raangha\f* taang ni mihoh rangdah nah datsiit suh tim uh tajeeka.
\v 11 Enoothong phoh ano ah mok miksuk ibah, seng loong ah laamang ni tongli; seng laamang adi khoom ino maani khoomli erah uh tajatke, mamah liidih laamang rah ih edook eh hoonthuk hali.
\p 
\v 12 Nga sah loong sen rangdah ah Kristo tungthoidi biin anaan hoon halan, erah raangtaan ih arah le ah raanghang.
\v 13 Hewah loong asuh raanghang ah langla, sen loong ih ejat ehan heh ephang dowa ih dook eje angta. Jaaro jaalah loong, ngah ih sen suh arah raanghang ah langla, sen loong ih Ethih warah ejen etan.
\p 
\v 14 Nga sah loong sen suh arah raanghang rah langla, sen loong ih heh Wah ah ejat ehan. Hewah loong, sen suh arah raanghang rah langla marah ephang dowa ih dook eje angla rah sen ih ejat ehan. Jaaro jaalah loong, ngah ih sen suh arah raanghang ah langla sen loong ah tarong; Rangte jengkhaap ah sen sak ni ang ano, sen loong ih Ethih warah ejen etan.
\p 
\v 15 Mongrep nyia arah mongrep adi timjih jeela erah suh nak ramka an. An mongrep asuh ramka ubah, an ih Hewah ah tah nookko.
\v 16 Marah mongrep dowa angla—rangdah tenthun raangtaan ih luulu angla, eno mina ih heh mik ih tup ha nyia heh ih timjih jamha, edoleh arah mongrep dowa jirep jaatrep raangtaan ih mina loong khuungpookla—erah mabah uh Hewah taangnawa tah angka; erah loong abah mongrep dowa.
\v 17 Mina mong mala mongrep nyia mongrep dowa timjih jeela erah loong ah emat eh ah; enoothong ngo ih Rangte thung jun ih reela erah bah roitang ih tong ah.
\s1 Kristo piiara
\p 
\v 18 Nga sah loong, rangkuh thoon tok ah ethok eh hala! Sen loong suh Kristo Piiara thok ha ngeh ban baat choi; amadi Kristo ra loong ah hantek ejen dong ih taha, erah raangtaan ih ejat ehi rangkuh thoon ah ethok eh hala ngeh ah.
\v 19 Erah mina loong ah amiimiisak di seng damdi rang choh roomsoomte tah ang rumka, erah raangtaan ih seng loong ah thinhaat ih hali; seng damdoh rang choh roomsoomte mok ang rumta bah seng damdoh eroong tong ih rum theng taha. Enoothong seng thinhaat heeno ba jat hi, neng loong ah seng mih tah angka ngeh ah.
\p 
\v 20 Enoothong Kristo ih sen sak ni Esa Chiiala daapkaat taha, eno sen thoontang ih amiisak ah jat han.
\v 21 Ngah ih arah raanghang rah sen loong ih amiisak ah lajat kanno tah raangkang; erah langla, sen ih erah jat ehan raangtaan ih ba raanghang, eno sen ih uh ejat ehan, eleek ah maatok uh amiisak taang dowa tah dong ra.
\p 
\v 22 Erah ang abah eleek ah ngo ah? Eleek loong abah Jisu suh Mesia tah angka liite loong ah. Erah likhiik mina loong abah Kristo Piiara—Hewah nyia Hesah neng enyi nyi dut haat rumha.
\v 23 Ngo ih Hesah tah kapka erah ih Hewah ah uh tah kapka; Ngo ih Hesah ah ekap eha erah ih Hewah uh ekap eha.
\p 
\v 24 Enooba, marah ephang di ruurang chaattu erah thin suh kamkam ang uh. Erah ruurang ah an ten nah thin ubah, an saarookwe Hesah nyia Hewah damdi roong thing tonglu.
\v 25 Eno Kristo heh teeteewah ih seng suh lathoon roidong kot suh kakham tahe.
\p 
\v 26 Ngah ih sen suh arah raanghang rah langla, ngo ih sen mokwaan chungha erah mina tiit ah raanghang.
\v 27 Enoothong sen loong suh bathong aleh Kristo ih Chiiala sen ten ni daapkaat taha. Timthan tuk Chiiala ah sen ten nah tongha, seng suh nyootsoot suh wahoh we jamtheng tah angka. Mamah liidih Chiiala ih jirep nyoot halan, eno marah nyoot halan erah amiisak, eleek tiit tah angka. Marah Chiiala ih nyoot halan erah ekap ih an, eno Kristo damdoh roongtong an.
\p 
\v 28 Elang ih ah, nga sah loong, heh damdoh roongtong an, erah doba heh teeteewah dong raaha Sa doh seng loong ah rakri ino tah hutong ke, erah damdi senghang sengchaan ah edong ih ah.
\v 29 An ih ejat ehu Kristo ah kateng; erah ang abah an ih ejat etheng, marah mina pun reela erah mina ah Rangte sah.
\c 3
\s1 Rangte suh asah
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Jn 1:12\x* Sok thaak an, Hewah ih seng timthan minchan hali! Heh minchan ah erathan rak seng ah Rangte sah ngeh jen poon thuk hali—eno amiimi di seng loong ah hesuh hesah langli. Neng loong ih seng ah tajat ri mamah liidih Rangte ah tajat rumka.
\v 2 Nga mongnook joonte loong, seng ah belam Rangte suh asah, enoothong seng mamah angte angli erah amadi tuk ih tajatke. Enoothong seng ih ejat ehi Kristo raaha doh seng ah heh likhiik angte angli, mamah liidih heh ah mamah angta erah likhiikkhiik ih kaptup ih.
\v 3 Marah mina ih Kristo asuh laalom la erah mina ih Kristo saata likhik heh uh sa chamcham angtheng.
\p 
\v 4 Ngo dala erah ih Rangte hotthe thetsiit ha erah ah thila, mamah liidih hotthe thetsiit ha rah rangdah.
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Jn 1:29\x* Sen ih ejat ehan Kristo ra taha rah rangdah saahaat ra taha,\f + \fr 3:5 \fq rangdah; \ft marah marah le ni seng rangdah raangha \f* eno heh di rangdah ah takah jeeka.
\v 6 Erah raang ih Kristo damdoh roong tongte loong ah rangdah laka dah theng; Enoothong marah mina daruh ela, erah mina ih heh ah mabah uh tah tupta nyia tajatta.
\p 
\v 7 Nga sah loong, ngo ih uh nak toom mokwaan han! Marah mina pun reela erah mina ah Kristo kateng angla likhiik heh uh kateng angla.
\v 8 Marah mina daruh ela erah mina ah Hakhoh juungbaan dabbi, mamah liidih Hakhoh juungbaan ih jaakhoh ni dook phang data. Rangte Sah ah erah thoi ih ra taha, marah Hakhoh juungbaan ih hoonta erah thet haat suh ra taha.
\p 
\v 9 Marah mina Rangte suh asah angla erah rangdah daruh tah daka, timnge liidih Rangte dang ajang ah neng damdi; edoleh Rangte ah neng Wah, erah thoidi neng ih rangdah ah daruh tah erumka.
\v 10 Rangte suh asah nyia Hakhoh juungbaan suh asah loong ah maama ang rum ah: Marah mina ah lapun reeka nyia wahoh lah minchanka rah Rangte suh asah tah angka.
\s1 Minchan mui etheng
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Jn 13:34\x* Jaakhoh ni chaattan jengkhaap ah arah: seng laktung nah minchan mui jaatjaat etheng.
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Rangph 4:8\x* Seng loong ah Keen likhiik nak angtheng; Heh ah Ethih Wah rah dakbi angthoi heh no Abel ah tek haatta. Keen ih heh ah tim suh tek haatta? Mamah liidih Keen reeraang ah ethih angta, eno heh no reeta ah epun angta.
\p 
\v 13 Phoh ano loong mongrep dowa mina loong ih mok miksuk hanbah nak paatja an.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Jn 5:24\x* Seng ih ejat ehi etek ah thinhaat eti eno ething roidong adi tongli; seng laktung ni minchan mui thaang ih arah jat hi. Marah mina ih phoh ano lah minchanka erah mina ah amadi uh etek chaan aphaan khui ni tong rumla.
\v 15 Marah mina ih hephoh heno miksuk ha erah mina ah mih tek haatte, eno sen ih ejat ehan mih tek haatte di lathoon roidong ah tajeeka ang ah.
\v 16 Minchan jat hi rah amah: Kristo ih heh teeteewah roidong ah seng raangtaan ih kota, erah likhiikkhiik seng eh uh sengphoh sengno raangtaan ih thing tongtheng!
\v 17 Seng changteng angli li ino sengphoh sengno ih timjih jamha erah etup ehi, ang abah uh neng suh tim uh takoke, erabah mamah ma jen chaang ih Rangte ah minchan ehang ngeh ah?
\v 18 Nga sah loong, seng dowa minchan ah jengkhaap luulu nyia tiitwaan luulu nah nak toom ang ah, erah nang ih amiisak minchan ah toom ang ah sengre sengraang nawa ih jen noisok theng toom ang ah.
\s1 Rangte re nah techan hoon
\p 
\v 19 Erah likhiikkhiik seng ah amiisak dabbi ngeh jat ih: seng loong Rangte ngathong nah rong tangtang jen ang ih.
\v 20 Sengthung sengtak ih seng loong mok dut haat heebah, seng ih ejat etheng sengthung sengtak nang ih Rangte ah elongthoon eno heh ih jirep roop jat ha.
\v 21 Erah raangtaan ih, mongnook joonte loong, sengthung sengtak ih seng asuh lamok damdak riibah, seng loong jinni tenchaan tenthun eje Rangte ngathong ni ah.
\v 22 Marah suhi, erah heh jin nawa echoh eli, mamah liidih seng ih heh jengdang ah ekap ehi eno heh thung punjih ah ere eli.
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt Jn 13:34; 15:12,17\x* Heh jengdang ah langla, seng ih Jisu Kristo suh hanpi ih nyia seng jaachi nah Kristo ih baat tahe likhiikkhiik minchan mui theng.
\v 24 Marah mina ih Rangte jengdang ah echaat eha erah mina ah heh damdi roong tongla, eno Rangte uh heh damdi roong tongla. Mamah liidih marah Rangte ih koh tahe Chiiala rah ih jatthuk hali, Rangte ah seng damdi roongtong hala.
\c 4
\s1 Amiisak chiiala nyia lalangka chiiala
\p 
\v 1 Nga mongnook joonte loong, ngo ih ang ah bah uh nga jinni Chiiala eje ngeh baat han bah thoontang nak hanpi an, enoothong thaak teeme eh an eno chiiala ah Rangte taangnawa tam ah ma nawa ah erah dong jat joh an. Mamah liidih mih khowamoong loong ah noongrep ni jen pheekhoom erumta.
\v 2 Rangte Chiiala elang tam talangka amah ih danjat an: marah ih Jisu Kristo ah mina ih hoon ano mongrep ni ra taha ngeh hanpiiha erah jinni Rangte taangnawa raaha rah Chiiala je ah.
\v 3 Enoothong marah ih Jisu ah mina ih hoon ano ra taha ngeh lah hanpiika bah, chiiala ah Rangte taangnawa ra haarah tah angka, enoothong heh taangnawa chiiala ah Kristo Raawah taangnawa ang ah; sen ih echaat etan eraak eha, erah amadi mongrep ni ejen raak ih taha.
\p 
\v 4 Enoothong nga sah loong, sen ah Rangte mina, eno sen ih lalangka khowah loong ah ejen etan, mamah liidih Chiiala marah sen taang ni angla erah Chiiala ah mongrep dowa chiiala nang ih echaan thoon.
\v 5 Lalangka khowah ih mongrep tiit baat ha erah mongrep nawa ih ba chaat ah, mamah liidih neng loong ah mongrep dowa.
\v 6 Enoothong seng loong ah Rangte mina. Marah mina ih Rangte jat eha erah mina loong ih seng jeng echaat ih ah; ngo Rangte mina tah angka erah mina ih seng jeng tah chaatka. Eno juuba amiisak Chiiala nyia lalangka chiiala ah jen dan baat ih.
\s1 Rangte aba minchan
\p 
\v 7 Mongnook joonte loong, seng jaachi nah minchan mui etheng, mamah liidih minchan ah Rangte taangnawa ra taha. Marah mina ih minchan eha erah Rangte suh asah nyia Rangte ah ejat eha.
\v 8 Marah mina ih lah minchanka erah mina ih Rangte ah tah jatka, mamah liidih Rangte ah minchan.
\v 9 Rangte ih heh Sah esiit luulu mongrep ni kaatthuk haano heh minchan ah noisok hali, erah doba heh jun ih seng roidong ah jen choh ih.
\v 10 Minchan abah arah: Rangte ah seng ih minchan ino tah angka, enoothong heh ih minchan heeno seng loong rangdah biin anaan raang ih heh Sah daapkaat taha.
\p 
\v 11 Mongnook joonte loong, Rangte ih emah minchan hali bah, seng laktung nah uh minchan mui etheng.
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Jn 1:18\x* Ngo mina eh uh Rangte ah etup muh, enoothong seng laktung nah minchan mui ibah, Rangte ah seng damdoh roong tongha, eno heh minchan rah seng minchan mui kino epunthoon ih hoonla.
\p 
\v 13 Seng loong ten ni kamkam angli seng ah Rangte damdi roong tongli eno Rangte ah seng damdi roongtong hala, mamah liidih heh ih seng loong suh heh Chiiala koh tahe.
\v 14 Seng ih etup eti eno wahoh suh baat ehi Hewah ih mongrep puipang suh heh Sah daapkaat taha ngeh ah.
\v 15 Jisu ah Rangte Sah mokli ibah, seng loong ah Rangte damdi roong tongli eno Rangte ah seng loong damdi roongtong hala.
\v 16 Rangte ih seng minchan hali ah seng teeteewah ih ejat ehi nyia ehanpi ehi .
\p Rangte ah minchan, marah mina minchan ni roong tongla erah Rangte damdi roong tongla eno Rangte uh neng damdi roong tongla.
\v 17 Minchan ah seng damdi ang ano epunthoon ih hoonla, dande saadoh seng tenchaan ih jenchap suh ah; seng loong suh tenchaan ah eje angjih, mamah liidih arah mongrep adi seng roidong ah Kristo angla likhiik angli.
\v 18 Minchan ni echo tah jeeka; epunthoon minchan rah ih echo tenthun tah dong thukka. Erah raangtaan ih ngo mina echo ela heh jinni minchan ah epunthoon tah angka, mamah liidih echo ela ah ehoocham thuktheng eje angthoi choola.
\p 
\v 19 Rangte ih phang minchan thoidi seng ih we minchanhi.
\v 20 Rangte ah minchan ehang li ino, phoh ano ah miksuk mok eh ibah, seng loong ah eleek. Erah raangtaan ih seng mik eh tup hi phoh ano ah lamok minchan keebah seng mik eh latupke Rangte ah batang aleh mamah ma mi minchan ih.
\v 21 Kristo ih koh tahe jengdang abah amah: Ngo ih Rangte minchan ha erah ih phoh ano nep uh minchan jaatjaat etheng.
\c 5
\s1 Mongrep jente ah seng
\p 
\v 1 Ngo ih Jisu ah Mesia ngeh hanpiiha erah mina ah Rangte sah; marah mina ih hewah rah minchan ha erah ih heh sah rah uh minchan eha.
\v 2 Rangte suh asah ah minchan ehi ngeh amah re eno jat ih: erah langla Rangte jengdang ah kap ino nyia Rangte ah minchan ino ah.
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Jn 14:15\x* Seng ih Rangte suh minchan liihi rah heh jengdang kap hi asuh liiha. Eno heh jengdang ah seng suh tah chaanka,
\v 4 mamah liidih timthan Rangte sah angla erah loong ih mongrep ah ejen eh ah. Eno seng tuungmaang je thaang ih mongrep ah jen ih.
\v 5 Mongrep ah ngo ih jen jen ah? Ngo ih Jisu ah Rangte Sah ngeh hanpiiha erah mina iba jen ah.
\s1 Jisu Kristo tiit di haaki
\p 
\v 6 Jisu Kristo ah langla heh juungtem joong nyia etek eta sih damdi raaha rah. Heh ah joong damdi luulu tah ra taha enoothong joong nyia sih damdi ra taha. Arah amiisak jo ngeh Chiiala heheh ih baat ha.
\v 7 Haaki ejom je ah:
\v 8 Chiiala, joong, nyia sih; eno arah ejom rah ih erarah tiitkhaap ah baat rumha.
\v 9 Mina tiitkhaap asuh seng ih hanpi ehi; enoothong Rangte tiitkhaap ah erah khotok di uh elongthoon, eno Heh ih heh sah tiitkhaap tiit ah ba baat ha.
\v 10 Erah raangtaan ih marah mina ih Rangte Sah asuh hanpiiha erah mina ten ni arah tiitkhaap ah tong ah; enoothong marah mina ih Rangte suh lah hanpiika, erah mina ih Rangte ah eleek ngeh hoonha, mamah liidih marah Rangte ih Heh sah roidong tiit baatta rah neng ih tah hanpi rumka.
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Jn 3:36\x* Roidong tiitkhaap ah arah: Rangte ih seng suh lathoon roidong koh tahe, lathoon roidong hiingroop ah heh Sah.
\v 12 Ngo jinni arah Sah ah jeela erah mina asuh arah roidong je ah; marah mina jinni arah Rangte Sah ah lah jeeka roidong ah tah jeeka.
\s1 Lathoon Roidong
\p 
\v 13 Sen jinni lathoon roidong ah eje ngeh toom jat an suh arah le ah raanghang—sen ih Rangte Sah hanpiihan tiit rah ah.
\v 14 Seng loong suh Rangte ngathong ni tenchaan eje, mamah liidih seng ih heh thungpun jun ih tiimjih suhi erah ekot ehe ngeh kamkam ih thun hi.
\v 15 Seng ih maatok suh ih eradi echaat ehali; seng ih ejat ehi arah tiit ah amiisak, erah uh ejat ehi maatok heh jinnah wa suh ih ekot ehe.
\p 
\v 16 Jengthaak asuh anphoh anno etek etheng sengseng rangdah lah daka rah mok tup ubah, sen ih rangsoom kottheng, Rangte ih roidong koh ah. Arah jengkhaap ah marah phoh ano etek etheng sengseng rangdah lah daka loong suh luulu. Enoothong etek lam nah siitte rangdah ah eje, erah likhiik loong asuh Rangte rangsoom koh an ngeh tabaat rumra.
\v 17 Timthan lalangka reeraang loong ah rangdah, Etek theng nah lathok siitka rangdah uh eje.
\p 
\v 18 Seng ih ejat ehi Rangte suh asah ih hedop hedop takah daka, mamah liidih Rangte Sah ih puipang ruh erumha, eno Ethih Warah ih neng tajen thet haat rumka.
\p 
\v 19 Seng ih ejat ehi arah mongrep ah Ethih Wah lakmong nah ang abah uh, seng loong ah Rangte suh asah.
\p 
\v 20 Ejat ehi Rangte Sah eraak ih taha, eno seng suh samjat etheng tenthun koh tahe, erah dowa ih Rangte ah amiisak ngeh jat hi. Seng loong ah amiisak Rangte damdi roong thingtongli—heh Sah Jisu Kristo damdi roong thingtongli. Eno arah ba amiisak Rangte nyia lathoon roidong.
\p 
\v 21 Ngaasuh ngaasah loong, sen teeteewah mih mokwaante rangte loong dowa haloh ih tong an!
